p.span: Themission of the Vineland Public Charter School is to provide a nurturing, supportive, creative and actively engaging environment for students and families that facilitates the development of well educated and responsible young adults with a life long love of learning.

/Registration Process
Applying to Attend the Vineland Public Charter School
To enter your child into the selection lottery for admission to the Vineland Public Charter School, you will need to fill out a Student Application.

span.span: Upon completion of the Application, please send it to:

p.span:
If you prefer, you may fax the completed application to:
856-691-1005.
